org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.parser.v2.geometries

Class MultiLineStringPropertyTypeBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.parser.v2.geometries.GeometryBinding
      • org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.parser.v2.geometries.MultiLineStringPropertyTypeBinding

  • public class MultiLineStringPropertyTypeBinding
extends GeometryBinding
    It parses a gml:multiLineStringProperty object. Example: 

     
 <multiLineStringProperty>
 <MultiLineString srsName="http://www.opengis.net/gml/srs/epsg.xml#4326">
 <lineStringMember>
 <LineString>
 <coord><X>56.1</X><Y>0.45</Y></coord>
 <coord><X>67.23</X><Y>0.98</Y></coord>
 </LineString>
 </lineStringMember>
 <lineStringMember>
 <LineString>
 <coord><X>46.71</X><Y>9.25</Y></coord>
 <coord><X>56.88</X><Y>10.44</Y></coord>
 </LineString>
 </lineStringMember>
 <MultiLineString>
 </multiLineStringProperty>
